      <scopecontent id="aspace_04d26f13f11f01b6433eeaa1fcce70fe">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of correspondence, journals, printed material, ephemera, and photographs relating to the history of Ethiopia and the current political and social conditions.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
